main event: An unidentified flying object was reported at Westover AFB, Massachusetts on January 23, 1967.
interesting points: The report concluded the sighting was likely a reflection,No photographs were included in the submission,The observer had attempted to capture a comet on camera instead capturing the UFO,The document includes references to Project Blue Book, a program investigating UFOs,The report indicates that two objects were not visible during the general outdoor photography.
witness description: The observer submitted a questionnaire with detailed responses about the sighting.
